title: Can't Patch 6.16
body: I can't patch 6.16 , it doesnt even patch. ive tried to repair logs but still doesnt do shiet. plz hlep me.

replies.body:
Patching issues can be caused by a number of different factors, but most are covered in our [Patching Issues Guide](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/202969434-Patching-Issues). I recommend starting there as a first step in resolving this issue, it's pretty quick and I'm confident it will help.

Let me know the results of those steps.
i fixed it, problem was that i didnt have enough storage on my disk, i had like 5 mb left, so i cleared a bit and i patched.
